# How to...

## Build the application
### Perequisites
I assume you are on UNIX-like environment with installed cabal and GHC that supports GHC2021

Internet access may be needed to download required dependences
### OK, now how to build it
Run the following command
> cabal build

Sometimes it may be necessary to add execution privilege to bash file.
> chmod +x burglar
## Run the application
Run following command

> ./burglar file_you_want_to.map

## Run the tests

> cabal test

## Information
This was created using:

GHC 9.6.7

Cabal 3.12.1.0

on WSL2/Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS
